He sold the moonstones to a couple players - who paid the big plat for some
odd reason. In the normal quest (Fangs to Tillin, Moonstones to Macneal,
Sell BB Stouts) you get almost a plat for 20 fangs - if your cha is like
mine - which is pretty high.

Sylly.
